{"tid":1105661,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"外國考車問題 好撚無助","createTime":"2019-04-14T05:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T02:32:08.000Z","uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"841d29320d00dadb52b186cc6b9f60fdb5f264d1","tid":1105661,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:25:01.000Z","msg":"我5年前過左筆試，但一路冇考牌<br />\n最近心血來潮想考，諗住去報路面試<br />\n點知佢話我個筆試太耐 要重新考 而且過左筆試仲要重新渣夠50個鐘先可以去考<br />\nok fine，因為我老母有車牌，所以叫佢拿拿林陪我渣夠50個鐘佢算，因為我本身學過好耐車 所以路面其實已經完全識渣 無謂哂錢再比師傅<br />\n點知我老母真係痴撚鳩線，怕撚死到仆街，一路渣一路係咁發脾氣，又要我渣低5-10km，又要我同其他車保持100米距離同埋100米就要剎車。一上高速/十字路口又係咁騰騰震，渣完又係咁話好驚死 又話發夢都夢到撞車死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但事實係我渣得無任何大錯 甚至可以話係穩<br />\n跟住我都發脾氣話唔撚洗陪我渣，幫我每日簽5個鐘簽到夠50個鐘就得，佢又唔撚肯 係度同我嘈<br />\n而家點撚好？因為我覺得自己已經夠quali去考，最多只需要搵師傅幫我練幾堂考試路線，如果我搵師傅幫我簽50個鐘要哂多成萬蚊hkd"},{"pid":"54e6cbe71c08e270c4ce0a69e0b4aa64dde0d77b","tid":1105661,"uid":191650,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"有冇過埋右考試"},{"pid":"1f3f4386921ad02685a292e896b6209ffb0f0ccd","tid":1105661,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"又係自己以為自己好勁系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3414bec218c386c9684fb9a768088672e0c1a8","tid":1105661,"uid":53466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e87b5db8df6ab8c90339eac7cb32c0b4f9d08dc","tid":1105661,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:29:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0356971772c7132d33410db37e4377f784c7d0a5","tid":1105661,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"十個學車九個覺得自己穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41887c796351053841ac0585ab4464f53777d4b5","tid":1105661,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"100米唔夠安全啵"},{"pid":"839dc2aab5928d59a198c9bad324c7cf72a6b786","tid":1105661,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"0356971772c7132d33410db37e4377f784c7d0a5","tid":1105661,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"十個學車九個覺得自己穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:36:34.000Z","msg":"我以前跟師傅學左幾十個鐘，所有rules都識哂，只係因為其他私事所以一路冇去考，我跟過兩個師傅 兩個都話我已經夠quali 基本上唔會犯錯，反而我老母渣車試過渣錯去對面黎既線，成日60既路渣左40，又撞過車etc"},{"pid":"9b52dd96765c11ae5f868f42fe91b99ce24ef3f8","tid":1105661,"uid":12703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"佢都係唔想你車死炸仆街仔"},{"pid":"d89aee39331f940ffe34fa0fc25473345934b05f","tid":1105661,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"比錢出去搵師傅算9數"},{"pid":"f0b77bd2753694b9296564336a619fad26b28e7e","tid":1105661,"uid":34174,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"當連登係咩，問埋d細路仔問題，借問聲樓主幾歲<br />\n一係就俾錢出去搵師傅<br />\n唔想俾錢就當老母係師傅咁尊重佢"},{"pid":"9f973a412df6d8608c3be66f2710a8f89787e05a","tid":1105661,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"澳洲？<br />\n去搵師傅啦，呢啲錢唔好慳"},{"pid":"d50a400ec665e1d9dd41ce0b42d697c8a450d030","tid":1105661,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330a7fd8f99db16f545ca67916b17e668c8276de","tid":1105661,"uid":182178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"一百米 10kph <br />\n危險左啲啵"},{"pid":"0ff5043fcd3f49c2207640441b0cb513858e8f16","tid":1105661,"uid":53312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50a400ec665e1d9dd41ce0b42d697c8a450d030","tid":1105661,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"cited